Class BidCandidateManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.enremmeta.rtb.BidCandidateManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Lot49Constants, Runnable

    public final class BidCandidateManager
extends Object
implements Runnable, Lot49Constants
    Manages the passing or failing of eligible Ads and their Tags for a given bid request, and sending the response.
